    • Method Detail

      • afterSetup

        protected void afterSetup()
        Description copied from class: JkPlugin
        Override this method to perform some actions, once the plugin has been setup by JkClass.setup() method.

        Typically, some plugins have to configure other ones (For instance, java plugin configures scaffold plugin to instruct what to use as a template build class). Those kind of configuration is better done here as the setup made in JkClass is likely to impact the result of the configuration.

        Overrides:
        afterSetup in class JkPlugin
